{"tid":1552332,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"唔駛理呢啲捉鬼撚","createTime":"2019-09-08T10:11:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-08T10:20:58.000Z","uid":116800,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"a51feac7e102f0df6a5a9337c033b2e8532e04fd","tid":1552332,"uid":116800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T10:11:43.000Z","msg":"你哋諗吓出post嗰啲係咩人?<br />\n<br />\n開呢啲post嘅目的係咩?<br />\n<br />\n我哋唔駛你分化 又唔係燒美領<br />\n<br />\n同埋差佬響地鐵站揮棍濫捕之後先有手足做嘢<br />\n你唔講?<br />\n<br />\n當你唔係有意嘅分化撚，身為冷氣軍師咁多意見點解唔落場去指點江山? 淨係識坐喺屋企批評，點解你唔落場講? 講啲咩失曬民意民氣，咩鬼佬唔撐我哋，屌你代表美國講話嗎？<br />\n<br />\n見3毛分化撚即unlike 上一頁 thanks"},{"pid":"4940d4ecef07daa404462dd3263dd0232729517a","tid":1552332,"uid":53568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T10:12:53.000Z","msg":"屌你老母又搞到個影像好暴力咁仲叫唔好捉<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bba118f2a72e6d4403aba0dd444491c35f4b1d30","tid":1552332,"uid":88123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T10:13:37.000Z","msg":"捉鬼撚食屎"},{"pid":"734ff3037de65f31dff605e59d55bd421177d3ad","tid":1552332,"uid":106276,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T10:14:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>今日係差佬係地鐵搞鳩路人<br />\n先有兄弟幫拖封站<br />\n唔撚好掉轉黎講<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">永不割席</span></span></blockquote>"},{"pid":"4067f685e8fa3eb5c8f01fe97fe06be9f8f50b25","tid":1552332,"uid":116800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4940d4ecef07daa404462dd3263dd0232729517a","tid":1552332,"uid":53568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T10:12:53.000Z","msg":"屌你老母又搞到個影像好暴力咁仲叫唔好捉<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"